insert.column:
{"FRA":"

Applique un frais un abonnement du compte de facturation.

Vous devrez slectionner une charge exceptionnelle (type autre) appliquer, avec la possibilit de remplacer le montant (cela gnrera une erreur si la charge ne permettent pas la surcharge du montant) et le libell.

Nous devrons slectionner un abonnement actif auquel appliquer le frais. Par dfaut, nous utiliserons l'abonnement actif le plus rcent factur sur les factures impayes. Vous pouvez fournir un filtre supplmentaire pour affiner la liste des abonnements. Ce filtre est en fait une expression qui doit s'value en une chane qui sera compare au code des abonnements dans la porte de recherche d'abonnement, l'aide de l'oprateur fourni. Lexpression aura accs au rejet de paiement, au paiement, aux entits du primtre (liste des factures, compte de facturation, compte client) et la liste des abonnements dans le primtre. Si aucun abonnement actif n'est trouv, le script chouera et une erreur sera remonte.

", "ENG":"

Applies a charge to a subscription of the billing account.

For the invoice to be valid, tested amount must pass the test.

You will have to select a one shot charge (type other) to apply, with the ability to override the amount (will raise an error if the charge doesnt allow amount override) and label.

We will need to select an active subscription to apply the charge to. By default, we will use the most recent active subscription invoiced on the unpaid invoices. You can provide an additional filter to narrow down the list of subscriptions. This filter is actually an expression that must evaluate to a string that will be compared to the code of subscriptions in the subscription search scope, using the provided operator. Expression will have access to the rejected payment, the payment, and the scope entities (list of invoices, billing account, customer account) and the list of subscriptions in the scope. If no active subscription is found, the script will fail and an error will be raised.

"}

changeSet.sql: UPDATE cpq_quote_product product SET mrr = subquery.total_calculated_amount FROM ( SELECT p.id as product_id, SUM( CASE WHEN cal.period_unit = 2 and cal.cal_type = 'PERIOD' THEN price.amount_with_tax / NULLIF(cal.period_length, 0) WHEN cal.period_unit = 5 and cal.cal_type = 'PERIOD' THEN (price.amount_with_tax * 365 / 12) / NULLIF(cal.period_length, 0) WHEN cal.period_unit IS NULL and cal.cal_type = 'YEARLY' THEN price.amount_with_tax * (select count(*) from cat_calendar_days d where d.calendar_id = cal.id) / 12 ELSE price.amount_with_tax END ) AS total_calculated_amount FROM cpq_quote_product p JOIN cpq_quote_article_line art ON art.quote_product_id = p.id JOIN cpq_quote_price price ON price.quote_article_line_id = art.id JOIN cat_charge_template ch ON ch.id = price.charge_template_id JOIN cat_calendar cal ON cal.id = ch.calendar_id WHERE price.price_type = 'RECURRING' AND price.price_level = 'PRODUCT' AND (cal.period_unit IS NULL OR cal.period_unit IN (2, 5)) GROUP BY p.id ) subquery WHERE product.id = subquery.product_id;

UPDATE cpq_quote q SET mrr = subquery.total_mrr FROM ( SELECT cq.id as quote_id, SUM(cqp.mrr) as total_mrr FROM cpq_quote cq JOIN cpq_quote_version cqv ON cqv.cpq_quote_id = cq.id JOIN ( SELECT cpq_quote_id, MAX(quote_version) as max_version FROM cpq_quote_version WHERE status = 'PUBLISHED' GROUP BY cpq_quote_id ) latest ON latest.cpq_quote_id = cqv.cpq_quote_id AND latest.max_version = cqv.quote_version JOIN cpq_quote_product cqp ON cqp.quote_version_id = cqv.id WHERE cqp.mrr IS NOT NULL GROUP BY cq.id ) subquery WHERE q.id = subquery.quote_id;

UPDATE cpq_order_product product SET mrr = subquery.total_calculated_amount FROM ( SELECT p.id as product_id, SUM( CASE WHEN cal.period_unit = 2 and cal.cal_type = 'PERIOD' THEN price.amount_with_tax / NULLIF(cal.period_length, 0) WHEN cal.period_unit = 5 and cal.cal_type = 'PERIOD' THEN (price.amount_with_tax * 365 / 12) / NULLIF(cal.period_length, 0) WHEN cal.period_unit IS NULL and cal.cal_type = 'YEARLY' THEN price.amount_with_tax * (select count(*) from cat_calendar_days d where d.calendar_id = cal.id) / 12 ELSE price.amount_with_tax END ) AS total_calculated_amount FROM cpq_order_product p JOIN order_article_line art ON art.order_product_id = p.id JOIN order_price price ON price.order_article_line_id = art.id JOIN cat_charge_template ch ON ch.id = price.charge_template_id JOIN cat_calendar cal ON cal.id = ch.calendar_id WHERE price.price_type = 'RECURRING' AND price.price_level = 'PRODUCT' AND (cal.period_unit IS NULL OR cal.period_unit IN (2, 5)) GROUP BY p.id ) subquery WHERE product.id = subquery.product_id;

UPDATE cpq_commercial_order ord SET mrr = subquery.total_mrr FROM ( SELECT o.id as order_id, SUM(cop.mrr) as total_mrr FROM cpq_commercial_order o JOIN cpq_order_product cop ON cop.order_id = o.id WHERE cop.mrr IS NOT NULL GROUP BY o.id ) subquery WHERE ord.id = subquery.order_id;
